                     <interp inst="t18090215-22-verdict124" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18090215-22-verdict124" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               Of stealing only
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18090215-22-punish125" type="punishmentDescription">
