                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090215-22-defend230 t18090215-22-punish125"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>SKIDDARD, <rs id="t18090215-22-verdict126" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18090215-22-verdict126" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. justice Bailey.</p>
